{
    "info": {
        "name": "Student Path — Absences API",
        "description": "## Setup\n\n1. Set `base_url` (e.g. `http://localhost:8000`).\n2. Run **Auth → verify-otp (guardian)** to fill `token`.\n3. Set `student_id` from **Parent — Students → GET /api/students** (student must be on an **active transport route** with an active driver).\n4. Call **Meta → GET /api/meta/absence-reasons** for picker codes: `medical`, `travel`, `family`, `other`.\n5. **Parent — Attendance schedule** → `GET /api/students/{id}/attendance-schedule` for the mobile calendar screen.\n6. **Enable arrival alerts** — run folder in order (daily timeline button: تفعيل تنبيهات الوصول).\n\n**Full guide:** `docs/ABSENCES_POSTMAN.md`\n\n## Parent flow\n\n`POST /api/absences` resolves the **subscribed driver** (student → transport route → driver), notifies driver + school staff, and marks matching trip roster rows absent.\n\n**422** if the student has no active route subscription (`student_id` validation error).\n\n## Driver flow\n\nLogin with **verify-otp (driver)** → `driver_token`. **GET /api/absences** returns absences where `driver_id` matches the linked driver.\n\n## Response fields (create / show)\n\n`id`, `student_id`, `driver_id`, `transport_route_id`, `start_date`, `end_date`, `reason`, `reason_code`, `reason_label_en`, `reason_label_ar`, `notes`, `driver_notified`, `driver_notified_at`, `school_notified`, `school_notified_at`, optional nested `student`, `driver`.\n\nSee `docs/API_V1_PARENT_TRANSPORT.md`.",
        "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
    },
    "variable": [
        {
            "key": "base_url",
            "value": "http://localhost:8000"
        },
        {
            "key": "token",
            "value": ""
        },
        {
            "key": "driver_token",
            "value": ""
        },
        {
            "key": "student_id",
            "value": "1"
        },
        {
            "key": "absence_id",
            "value": "1"
        },
        {
            "key": "absence_reason",
            "value": "travel"
        },
        {
            "key": "absence_start_date",
            "value": "2026-06-06"
        },
        {
            "key": "absence_end_date",
            "value": "2026-06-06"
        },
        {
            "key": "schedule_year",
            "value": "2026"
        },
        {
            "key": "schedule_month",
            "value": "6"
        },
        {
            "key": "timeline_date",
            "value": "2026-06-06"
        },
        {
            "key": "trip_id",
            "value": "TRP-1"
        },
        {
            "key": "fcm_token",
            "value": "sample_fcm_token_replace_with_device_token_from_firebase"
        }
    ],
    "item": [
        {
            "name": "Auth",
            "description": "OTP login only. Phone must exist in `users`. Use `type_user`: `guardian` for parent, `driver` for driver.",
            "item": [
                {
                    "name": "POST /api/auth/send-otp (guardian)",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Accept",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            },
                            {
                                "key": "Content-Type",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            }
                        ],
                        "url": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/send-otp",
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "raw",
                            "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"7701234567\",\n  \"type_user\": \"guardian\"\n}"
                        }
                    }
                },
                {
                    "name": "POST /api/auth/verify-otp (guardian)",
                    "event": [
                        {
                            "listen": "test",
                            "script": {
                                "type": "text/javascript",
                                "exec": [
                                    "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                                    "  try {",
                                    "    const j = pm.response.json();",
                                    "    const t = j.data && (j.data.token || j.data.access_token);",
                                    "    if (t) { pm.collectionVariables.set('token', t); }",
                                    "  } catch (e) {}",
                                    "}"
                                ]
                            }
                        }
                    ],
                    "request": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Accept",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            },
                            {
                                "key": "Content-Type",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            }
                        ],
                        "url": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/verify-otp",
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "raw",
                            "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"7701234567\",\n  \"code\": \"1234\",\n  \"type_user\": \"guardian\"\n}"
                        }
                    }
                },
                {
                    "name": "POST /api/auth/send-otp (driver)",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Accept",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            },
                            {
                                "key": "Content-Type",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            }
                        ],
                        "url": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/send-otp",
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "raw",
                            "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"7709876543\",\n  \"type_user\": \"driver\"\n}"
                        }
                    }
                },
                {
                    "name": "POST /api/auth/verify-otp (driver)",
                    "event": [
                        {
                            "listen": "test",
                            "script": {
                                "type": "text/javascript",
                                "exec": [
                                    "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                                    "  try {",
                                    "    const j = pm.response.json();",
                                    "    const t = j.data && (j.data.token || j.data.access_token);",
                                    "    if (t) { pm.collectionVariables.set('driver_token', t); }",
                                    "  } catch (e) {}",
                                    "}"
                                ]
                            }
                        }
                    ],
                    "request": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Accept",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            },
                            {
                                "key": "Content-Type",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            }
                        ],
                        "url": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/verify-otp",
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "raw",
                            "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"7709876543\",\n  \"code\": \"1234\",\n  \"type_user\": \"driver\"\n}"
                        }
                    }
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "Meta",
            "item": [
                {
                    "name": "GET /api/meta/absence-reasons",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "GET",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Accept",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            },
                            {
                                "key": "Authorization",
                                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
                            }
                        ],
                        "url": "{{base_url}}/api/meta/absence-reasons"
                    },
                    "description": "Returns `[{ code, label_en, label_ar }, ...]` for the mobile reason picker. Use `code` in POST/PATCH body (`medical`, `travel`, `family`, `other`)."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "Parent — Students",
            "description": "Pick `student_id` from the list. Student must be assigned to an active transport route.",
            "item": [
                {
                    "name": "GET /api/students",
                    "event": [
                        {
                            "listen": "test",
                            "script": {
                                "type": "text/javascript",
                                "exec": [
                                    "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                                    "  try {",
                                    "    const j = pm.response.json();",
                                    "    const items = j.data && (j.data.items || j.data);",
                                    "    if (Array.isArray(items) && items.length && items[0].id) {",
                                    "      pm.collectionVariables.set('student_id', String(items[0].id));",
                                    "    }",
                                    "  } catch (e) {}",
                                    "}"
                                ]
                            }
                        }
                    ],
                    "request": {
                        "method": "GET",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Accept",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            },
                            {
                                "key": "Authorization",
                                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
                            }
                        ],
                        "url": "{{base_url}}/api/students"
                    }
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "Parent — Attendance schedule",
            "description": "Mobile screen: جدول الحضور و الغياب — monthly summary, calendar statuses, recent absences & delays.",
            "item": [
                {
                    "name": "GET /api/students/{id}/attendance-schedule",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "GET",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Accept",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            },
                            {
                                "key": "Authorization",
                                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
                            }
                        ],
                        "url": "{{base_url}}/api/students/{{student_id}}/attendance-schedule?year={{schedule_year}}&month={{schedule_month}}&recent_limit=10"
                    },
                    "description": "Returns `summary` (counts + `present_color` / `absence_color` / `late_color`), `status_legend`, `calendar[]` (date + status + `status_color` + `status_icon`), `recent_events[]` (with `color` + `icon`). Colors: present `#00796B`, absent `#D32F2F`, late `#5D4037`."
                },
                {
                    "name": "GET /api/students/{id}/attendance-schedule (current month)",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "GET",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Accept",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            },
                            {
                                "key": "Authorization",
                                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
                            }
                        ],
                        "url": "{{base_url}}/api/students/{{student_id}}/attendance-schedule"
                    }
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "Parent — Daily timeline",
            "description": "Mobile screen: الجدول الزمني — 4 milestones with status colors (green completed/boarded, grey scheduled, red absent).",
            "item": [
                {
                    "name": "GET /api/students/{id}/daily-timeline",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "GET",
                        "header": [
